data.description:
Hunter's paradise!! This mostly wooded 100+ acre tract is just the place if you love to hunt. QDM (Quality Deer Management) has been practiced on this property since 2011 that includes five food plots, 2-600 pound Banks gravity feeders & 1 Banks Stump Vision Whitetail Properties Edition 3 man blind. There are several fruit trees that have been planted and all 5 food plots have had several thousand pounds of lime over the years. The property has multiple creeks running through it as well. There is an Amish built log cabin with 2 loft area that is run by a generator that will stay with the property and an additional 12x20 storage barn for your mower and ATV or whatever you need it for. The owner has harvested many trophy whitetails on this property over the years which can be seen on our website. Whether you are looking for whitetails or turkeys this is the place you have been waiting for.

John Deere 1025R Sub-compact tractor with 48" Brush Hog and 48" Disc and Honda Foreman 500 4-wheeler can be purchased separately.

Do not walk property without an agent present and all agents must call to set up appointment.
